{
  "stem": "20616.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He came from very humble background, from some little village somewhere in the Eifel.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I believe his father was a cattle dealer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he started to work at a bank and worked himself up as a manager or assistant manager of the branch of the Glasner Bank, which is a leading chain-- leading bank in Germany.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then he became independent and became a-- he formed his own private bank and it was called [GERMAN], the Private Bank of Triere.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it occupied the lower floor of the house where they lived.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I remember very well as a child when I visited them, I played in the office and they had the high tables where the bookkeepers stood-- or-- or sat-- on high stools.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was allowed to play with the typewriter-- manual typewriters, of course, at that time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I had a good time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My grandfather had his private office, which I was never to enter when he had someone there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But my grandfather was very doting and when I was there in the office and there was no one there, he always came in and talked to me.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he also was a very warm person.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I loved to go on walks with him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my grandfather also was a very devout religious person and he prayed twice a day and after each meal.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he talked to me about the Jewish religion.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And one thing stood out in my mind very much.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He always said, as a Jew, you have to be-- work twice as hard, be twice as smart, and be twice as ethical as anyone else and then you can exist in Germany and do well in Germany.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But you always have to remember that.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
